Global Insect Repellent Active Ingredients Market Insights
Insect Repellent Active Ingredients Market size was valued at USD 4.96 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 8.9 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.6% from 2024 to 2030.

Insect Repellent Active Ingredients Market Overview
The insect repellent active ingredients market has witnessed substantial growth in recent years due to increased awareness regarding vector-borne diseases like malaria, dengue, and Zika virus. The global market for insect repellent active ingredients is projected to grow significantly, driven by rising consumer preference for preventive health measures and expanding outdoor recreational activities. Natural and plant-based ingredients are gaining popularity, particularly in regions with environmentally conscious consumers. By 2028, the market is expected to reach a valuation of $8.5 billion, reflecting a CAGR of 6.5%. The market is influenced by factors such as innovation in formulations, rising health concerns, and regulatory standards.

